  Weighted overlays allow you to give values
  or weights to landscape characteristics.
  These weights are then added up for each 
  grid cell to produce a result map.

  Example:
    You give the following weights:
       map        category   weight
       --------   --------  --------
       soil.ph       1         10
       soil.ph       2          5
       landuse       1         12
       landuse       2         30
       geology       1          6
       geology       2          9

